eed</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车电池制造商宁德时代预计2023年利润将跃升48%，保持相对于竞争对手的巨大优势</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3250390/chinese-ev-battery-maker-catl-expects-2023-profit-jump-much-48-cent-it-maintains-huge-advantage-over?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>全球最大的电动汽车电池制造商宁德时代新能源科技（CATL）预计，受益于全球电动汽车普及率的不断提高，2023年净利润将攀升高达48%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 05:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3250390/chinese-ev-battery-maker-catl-expects-2023-profit-jump-much-48-cent-it-maintains-huge-advantage-over?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>上海大爆炸：火箭试验造成3名工人受伤并吓坏了居民</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3250384/big-bang-shanghai-rocket-test-injures-three-workers-and-spooks-residents?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>SpaceX 的竞争对手 LandSpace 表示，压力测试结果符合预期，没有发生爆炸，也没有造成员工严重受伤。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 05:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3250384/big-bang-shanghai-rocket-test-injures-three-workers-and-spooks-residents?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国商会负责人：在台美国公司通过选择当地合作伙伴来应对地缘政治和供应链风险</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3250302/us-firms-taiwan-fight-geopolitical-supply-chain-risks-picking-local-partners-investments-grow-amcham?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>台湾官方数据显示，去年美国对台投资达到 9.32 亿美元，高于 2022 年的 3.98 亿美元，创下 2008 年以来的最高单年总额。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 02:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3250302/us-firms-taiwan-fight-geopolitical-supply-chain-risks-picking-local-partners-investments-grow-amcham?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>尽管制造业活动反弹，中国经济到2024年仍遭遇“软启动”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3250366/chinas-manufacturing-activity-rebounds-slightly-january-remains-contraction?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>周三公布的数据显示，1月份中国官方制造业采购经理人指数小幅上升至49.2，但该指数连续第四个月处于收缩状态。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 01:36:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3250366/chinas-manufacturing-activity-rebounds-slightly-january-remains-contraction?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国深圳公布了 2024 年经济和工业复苏的大胆科技计划</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3250323/chinas-shenzhen-reveals-bold-tech-plans-economic-industrial-resurgence-2024?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在应对美国主导的科技限制的同时，深圳计划今年在战略性新兴产业领域实现超过2090亿美元的工业总产值。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 23:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3250323/chinas-shenzhen-reveals-bold-tech-plans-economic-industrial-resurgence-2024?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国国会考虑新立法进一步限制对中国科技行业的投资</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3250360/us-congress-considers-new-legislation-further-restrict-investment-chinese-tech-sectors?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>听证会是在乔·拜登总统禁止美国投资四个中国科技行业的行政命令的基础上举行的；目击者敦促立法者利用现有的权力，而不是建立新的机制。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 22:42:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3250360/us-congress-considers-new-legislation-further-restrict-investment-chinese-tech-sectors?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>暴风雪和极端天气可能会扰乱中国的农历新年旅行</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3250317/blizzards-and-extreme-weather-could-disrupt-chinas-lunar-new-year-travel?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>气象部门表示，预计春节期间，全国大部分地区将受到暴风雪、冻雨和强降雨的影响，这种“复杂”的天气条件可能会对交通运输产生“重大影响”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 22:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3250317/blizzards-and-extreme-weather-could-disrupt-chinas-lunar-new-year-travel?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>欧盟印太论坛将缺席未受邀的美国和中国</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3250359/european-union-forum-indo-pacific-will-lack-us-and-china-which-were-not-invited?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>不清楚去年出席会议的华盛顿为何没有参与布鲁塞尔；北京也将被遗漏，但从未被包括在内。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 19:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3250359/european-union-forum-indo-pacific-will-lack-us-and-china-which-were-not-invited?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>智库报告称，各种问题将导致“中国痛苦的一年”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3250357/variety-problems-will-result-vexing-year-china-says-think-tank-report?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>一个关键挑战是：尽管人口减少、社会安全网遭到破坏、政府政策不断变化、投资者感到不安，但仍要恢复信任和信心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 19:10:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3250357/variety-problems-will-result-vexing-year-china-says-think-tank-report?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>红海袭击事件：观察人士称，美中会谈后没有正式提及，但“可能”取得进展</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3250328/red-sea-attacks-no-official-mention-after-us-china-talks-progress-likely-have-been-made-observers?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>王毅和杰克·沙利文在曼谷会面后的官方声明没有提及关键海上走廊的袭击事件，一位分析人士称这个问题“太重要，无法回避”，但“太敏感，无法提及”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 16:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3250328/red-sea-attacks-no-official-mention-after-us-china-talks-progress-likely-have-been-made-observers?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国在智慧港口建设中争夺全球主导地位</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3250341/china-stakes-global-dominance-race-build-intelligent-ports?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国首个全自动港口集装箱码头自上个月开业以来已经创下了纪录。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 15:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3250341/china-stakes-global-dominance-race-build-intelligent-ports?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>国内外激烈